				README
				------

This file contains an index to the other files in this directory:

	README			- This file, a guide to the directory contents
	Clipboard		- The PC/GEOS Clipboard API
	DebugTips		- Tips on debugging UI & object code
	InterfaceConstruction	- How to put together, configure generic objects
				  & trees so as to able to construct an
				  application interface
	MethodConventions	- Proper doc conventions for methods
	Presentation		- Doug's 2-hour presentation outline on the UI
	PtrImage		- Ptr Image API
	QuickTransfer		- Quick Transfer API
	SDKIssues		- Misc things related to SDK
	ScreenSaver		- Screen Saver API
	V1.0_to_V2.0_conversion	- What a developer needs to do to port V1.0
				  code to run under the V2.0 PC/GEOS UI.


